37
00:02:21.521 --> 00:02:23.389
It gives you a shared
repository of knowledge.

38
00:02:23.389 --> 00:02:26.444
So as people leave the organization and
new people come in,

39
00:02:26.444 --> 00:02:28.165
you've got it all written down.

40
00:02:28.165 --> 00:02:29.946
And it also improves collaboration.

41
00:02:29.946 --> 00:02:33.561
And it can empower people as well,
cuz it teaches them best practice and

42
00:02:33.561 --> 00:02:35.198
what to do and things like that.

43
00:02:35.198 --> 00:02:38.321
And a part of that should
